description:
What's the best shampoo? What's the best toothpaste? What's the best soap? Unlock the secrets to choosing the best personal care products with Barbara O'Neil! In this quick, informative video, Barbara explores selecting the healthiest types of soaps, and shares tips on harmful chemicals that can cause to hair loss. Discover the natural benefits of coconut oil for conditioning and the wisdom of using charcoal as toothpaste. Strengthen your teeth and prioritize your skin by choosing natural soaps. Barbara also highlights the importance of being mindful of the chemicals in laundry products and offers a solution for toxin-free clothing. Learn how to take care of your body and make informed choices for healthier living!
